                "inputAnchors": [],
                "inputs": {
                    "llmModel": "chatZhipuAI",
                    "llmMessages": [
                        {
                            "role": "system",
                            "content": "<p>你是一名专业商务邮件助手，擅长根据沟通场景、收件对象和语气起草中文客户邮件。邮件应礼貌、清晰、具体，有明确下一步，并符合中文商务沟通习惯。避免夸大承诺、绝对化表达和不必要的施压措辞；对于未提供的信息，不要虚构具体价格、日期或条款。</p>"
                        },
                        {
                            "role": "user",
                            "content": "<p>请根据以下信息起草中文客户邮件：</p><p>邮件场景：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.scenario\" data-label=\"$form.scenario\">{{ $form.scenario }}</span></p><p>收件对象：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.recipient\" data-label=\"$form.recipient\">{{ $form.recipient }}</span></p><p>核心要点：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.keyPoints\" data-label=\"$form.keyPoints\">{{ $form.keyPoints }}</span></p><p>语气：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.tone\" data-label=\"$form.tone\">{{ $form.tone }}</span></p><p>草稿数量：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.variantCount\" data-label=\"$form.variantCount\">{{ $form.variantCount }}</span></p><p>要求：生成指定数量的邮件草稿，每版都需要包含邮件主题、正文和落款。正文要围绕核心要点展开，语气贴合收件对象与场景，并给出清晰、礼貌的下一步行动建议。若关键事实缺失，请使用可替换占位表达，不要编造。</p>"
                        }
                    ],
                    "llmEnableMemory": false,
                    "llmReturnResponseAs": "userMessage",
                    "llmStructuredOutput": [
                        {
                            "key": "variants",
                            "type": "jsonArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "{\n    \"subject\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"邮件主题\"\n    },\n    \"body\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"邮件正文\"\n    },\n    \"signoff\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"礼貌落款\"\n    }\n}",
                            "description": "多版客户邮件草稿，每版包含主题、正文和落款"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "tips",
                            "type": "stringArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "发送前检查建议、个性化补充建议或跟进提醒"
                        }
                    ],
                    "llmUpdateState": "",
                    "llmModelConfig": {
